{"tid":423980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐 HK Express 大爆...","createTime":"2017-10-04T10:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T13:02:47.000Z","uid":69930,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea981c1522f51a502361ac7594be1c9cc2d066c","tid":423980,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l6sag354\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl6sag354&h=c4ddf42b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1704233719618374&amp;id=737074803000942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1704233719618374%26id%3D737074803000942&d=dxc1uezZ%2FGoTHL6prBmJHNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9748a4b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1704233719618374&amp;id=737074803000942</a><br />\n<br />\n香港01<br />\n香港快運（HK Express）近日爆出人手嚴重不足，導致黃金周18班航班需要臨時取消。政府亦明言情況不理想，責成香港快運要在一周內提交報告。<br />\n<br />\n有香港快運空姐向《香港01》透露，由於空中服務員人手非常緊張，導致機組人員編更上非常混亂，「直情今日都唔知今日事」，隨時一通電話就要改變飛行時間及目的地。她又提到，香港快運對員工發放消息「非常封閉」，就連公司「喜訊」都不會作內部通知，「有新航點我都係睇出面啲旅遊網先知」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/123377/HK-Express空姐大吐苦水-編更混亂-內部封閉-今日唔知今日事-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F123377%2FHK-Express%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%90%E8%8B%A6%E6%B0%B4-%E7%B7%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82-%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%B0%81%E9%96%89-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%8B-&d=dxc1uezZ%2FGoTHL6prBmJHNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b3a97ff8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/123377/HK-Express空姐大吐苦水-編更混亂-內部封閉-今日唔知今日事-</a>"},{"pid":"1fbb62593d592ebb6f135dce31359c7d36ba74f1","tid":423980,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"真垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47dd59ac5b6c96b1c6f82